ps://lih.kg/1295758\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295758</a>"},{"pid":"3fe9066308c1ae710635a3ca67ea14d06547bb53","tid":1297785,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:48:07.000Z","msg":"大家繼續行落去<br />\n做麥兜又好 做麥嘜又好<br />\n大家都係同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我知道今晚既麥兜好偉大<br />\n希望你地原諒麥嘜既一時貪玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd217a9277bb9292f222d52f9f0220c8fdd743ed","tid":1297785,"uid":68080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:51:28.000Z","msg":"加油啊大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n前路漫長<br />\n我地要一齊行落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29dbb536c7b847befd6b1afdd91b7cb17b503f9a","tid":1297785,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:52:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家記住請先fact check 立場live 蘋果live 如果真係有事 無理由傳媒會唔知</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d623adc1c28a7a41fc23d935e6dd320aec1b2120","tid":1297785,"uid":42852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:53:32.000Z","msg":"最新白宮聯署！要求美國國會立即通過《香港人權民主法案》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295654\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295654</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我今日就做咗豬<br />\n對唔住大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不撒不散"},{"pid":"92f7774acc6f618776e5640d198796521f49a60e","tid":1297785,"uid":267027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:59:00.000Z","msg":"豬來了"},{"pid":"72be6a2cd688393eab775370364f8e97519e9a5d","tid":1297785,"uid":181035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:50:46.000Z","msg":"